response.overview: The lives of friends Daníel and Randver get much more complicated when they are forced to deliver a home order from the store where they work: a tube television… which they have to carry by hand. What should have been a short and simple trip turns into an ordeal when they get lost on Úlfarsfell and encounter all kinds of difficulties—such as mysterious elf-women, enigmatic beings, and pretty girls.
response.title: The Lord of the Tube Television
